rules.ruleName: CDL007 Trailer Paid Amt Does Not Match With Detail Paid Amt
rules.definition:
{"id":"","name":"SQL query","ruleType":"SQLQuery","ruleTypeLabel":"SQL Query","active":"Yes","severity":"Medium","dataQualityDimension":"Validity","ruleQuery":"select * from (
select Detail__Paid__Amt, Trailer__Paid__Amt 
from 
(select CDL007 Trailer__Paid__Amt from CAST_PC_hdr_trlr_chk where 
		cdl001 = 'TR') t,
(select sum(cdlpc037) Detail__Paid__Amt from CAST_PC_DATA) c) a  
where Detail__Paid__Amt <> Trailer__Paid__Amt","ruleConditionType":"bad records","operation":"<","threshold":"0","unit":"Percentage","percentage":"0","columnNames":"","successCriteria":"No bad records found","recordsCount":"0","workSchemaId":"0","dataQuery":"select count(*) from CAST_PC_hdr_trlr_chk"}

 (select columnname, nullcount,  rowcount as Total_Cnt,
100.00 - (nullif(nullcount, 1)/(nullif(rowcount, 1))*100) as Not_Null_Percent
from PC_DP)
select columnname, nullcount as Total__Null__Count, total_cnt as Total__Rec__Count from null_cnt_table
where columnname in
